        <statement>
            <p>
                Given that <m>A\, (6,8)</m>, <m>B\, (8,8)</m>, <m>C\, (12,8)</m>, <m>D\, (14,2)</m> and <m>E\, (10,0)</m> are the verticies of the pentagon, find the verticies of its image after an enlargement with origin as the centre and scale factor of:
